330
00:16:28,055 --> 00:16:30,140
Wat doe jij, eikel?

331
00:16:30,224 --> 00:16:31,433
Probeer de trein op te blazen.

332
00:16:31,517 --> 00:16:33,936
Dingen laten ontploffen,
